063,"uid":3873,"like":96,"dislike":0,"score":96,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T09:24:04.000Z","msg":"初時睇我以為係爺孫黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfc448eebcef7d42dd16fae0f56322793c9e7d08","tid":759063,"uid":96,"like":164,"dislike":0,"score":164,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T09:25:20.000Z","msg":"又窮又老都仲生 你估你賭王咩<br />\n分分鐘個女中學都未畢業就冇左個老豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d21ca6b1172a0e8a4d395354959b038c69d84c64","tid":759063,"uid":166474,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T09:26:32.000Z","msg":"三個老綜加埋租津成皮幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39890c15d994ffe994e3991d706fbd6cf877fb8e","tid":759063,"uid":55913,"like":82,"dislike":0,"score":82,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T09:26:37.000Z","msg":"69歲仲扯得起<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf159d09d38193a05bcabe5bd65cc0c1cb4e3808","tid":759063,"uid":28765,"like":74,"dislike":0,"score":74,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T09:26:37.000Z","msg":"成70歲先生明顯都冇計劃同安排下一代既幸福架啦"},{"pid":"99287a176688ba616a4f1a7a17d0bc23905057d8","tid":759063,"uid":108696,"like":87,"dislike":0,"score":87,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T09:26:58.000Z","msg":"正垃圾, 又窮又無腦, 制做社會垃圾<br />\n害死個女..."},{"pid":"2f6a1b29ff731bfa9e764c4e00587f90f87f9fef","tid":759063,"uid":55593,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T09:27:46.000Z","msg":"咁撚老屋又冇錢又冇仲學人生仔，好撚嘢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aa81f792318897afc3eefc5ac45ebf5f27083b4","tid":759063,"uid":3167,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T09:28:29.000Z","msg":"屌仲好意思上報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e4e6c3e4b6dfd3a9dfc26bdbc06a1776b2a3e09","tid":759063,"uid":160102,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T09:29:37.000Z","msg":"死廢老你生黎做乜？"},{"pid":"fe2c9016b0a97b577f064ad502cc1b90ad0a8573","tid":759063,"uid":99700,"like":294,"dislike":1,"score":293,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T09:31:04.000Z","msg":"一個七十五歲的老人去做健康檢查。檢查途中，老人不斷向醫生炫耀他新婚的妻子多好多好。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;他才二十五歲！&rdquo;老人叫道，&ldquo;我們結婚四個月，你知道她對我有多忠誠，她無時無刻不需要我，粘我粘到我都感到厭煩了！&rdquo;&ldquo;而且，&rdquo;老人又說，&ldquo;告訴你，她最近懷孕了！&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n醫生靜靜地聽著，一言不發，&ldquo;怎麼樣？&rdquo;老人得意洋洋地說，&ldquo;不錯罷？&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n醫生抬起頭，看了他一眼。&ldquo;這讓我想起一位失散多年的朋友。他跟我說過一個故事，是他在非洲狩獵時遇上的事。當時他在草原上遇到一頭獅子，他立刻從背上抓下槍來瞄準。然而，他立刻發現他錯了，他拿到的是雨傘，不是槍。這時已經太遲，獅子正站在他面前，就要撲過來，他只好把雨傘扛在肩上，使盡吃奶的力氣&lsquo;砰砰砰&rsquo;大叫三聲，奇跡發生了，那獅子竟然倒下死掉啦。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;狗屎，這怎麼可能&rdquo;老人大叫，&ldquo;那一定是別人幹的！&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;我也這麼認為&rdquo;醫生說....."},{"pid":"62721437defa78be1a25f01dae117056c54a78a6","tid":759063,"uid":52946,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T09:32:31.000Z","msg":"痴撚線 75歲就唔好害人啦"},{"pid":"05f6edd95f25ea8e08a9a1ea2cecc90bd1ae0155","tid":759063,"uid":29660,"like":106,"dislike":0,"score":106,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T09:37:25.000Z","msg":"同齡小朋友問起上黎「呢個你爺爺啊」<br />\n答爸爸會好尷尬 俾人恥笑"},{"pid":"b47c1392389da63bce793e193e677b9eebf84b34","tid":759063,"uid":81737,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T09:40:49.000Z","msg":"仲有教呢 問題少女就係呢到出黎"},{"pid":"e890265c54ab56960bd30627bef5b7144888310d","tid":759063,"uid":62650,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T09:44:24.000Z","msg":"好羨慕 69歲仲有人同佢生仔"},{"pid":"d4617a53bfb250a8fcaf877fd45400ff7760ab8d","tid":759063,"uid":145923,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T09:48:13.000Z","msg":"驗下DNA好D"},{"pid":"2404e6345f31733b83379f1600996493f1dc3ab4","tid":759063,"uid":136662,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"bf